To help strengthen the voice of the European business community, EuroCham have operated in affiliation with a number of European National Business Associations based in Vietnam including:&#xd;
1) German Business Association in Vietnam (GBA)&#xd;
2) French Chamber of Commerce and Industry in Vietnam (CCIFV)&#xd;
3) Dutch Business Association Vietnam (DBAV)&#xd;
4) Belgium Luxembourg Chamber of Commerce in Vietnam (BeluxCham)&#xd;
5) Italian Chamber of Commerce in Vietnam (ICHAM)&#xd;
Spainish Business Group (SpainChamVN)&#xd;
6) Central and Eastern European Chamber of Commerce in Vietnam (CEEC)&#xd;
7) Nordic Chamber of Commerce Vietnam (NordCham) (Hanoi chapter)
